 to be hot and sunny today. It also said there would be dry, sunny spells, scattered hail showers and drizzle tomorrow. Of course, snow showers and sleet showers are much better than thundery showers and wintry showers. In Hokkaido, we had fog and a hail shower earlier but now, it's sunny. Yesterday, I forgot my umbrella and raincoat so I got caught in a rain shower while touring the attractions there and a snow shower on my way to the hotel."},{"pid":"80e0a9005cffb7e300d001ea06dd4feeb29db3cf","tid":2015403,"uid":8599,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T13:00:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />andy哥介紹你先知"},{"pid":"0d25eed338f78937f648f8eae2365a02894d9a00","tid":2015403,"uid":2861,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T13:04:59.000Z","msg":"去日本返工我係香港算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n難得有地方係奴隸過香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a10fdece4daf8466cdabfc319749c760315bf9cb","tid":2015403,"uid":27251,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T01:54:38.000Z","msg":"就讓歐冠隨風<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"529b7a9f570f9c6c523091c7eee4850b5d3b9a3c","tid":2015403,"uid":277751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T04:35:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}